highlights.text: Perunggu has the most spots on Viral Songs Indonesia. “Pikiran Yang Matang” is the highest at #38.
“About You” by The 1975 has been on Viral Songs Indonesia the longest, at 371 days straight.
“Cinta Dari Seberang” by Yaya Nadila and Zinidin Zidan is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Indonesia at #92.
“XXL” by LANY is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Indonesia, up 18 spots at #45.
